<div><div><h2>Hindustan Zinc Q2 profit dives nearly 30% to  1,815 crore</h2></div><div>hindustan zinc ltd reported a 29.8% fall in second-quarter profit on monday dented by higher expenses. net profit dropped to  1815 crore ($247.43 million) in the quarter ended 30 september from  2584 crore a year earlier the zinc miner said. revenue from operations fell 10% to  4777 crore. however mined metal production in the quarter rose six percent.</div></div>